 where to print this info, as for now the `describe()` method prints the width info:\r\n```\r\n>>> print Particle.from_pdgid(511).describe()\r\nName: B          ID: 511          Fullname: B0             Latex: $B^{0}$\r\nMass  = 5279.63 +/- 0.15 MeV\r\nWidth = 4.330e-10 +/- 1.1e-12 MeV\r\nI (isospin)       = 1/2    G (parity)        = 0      Q (charge)       = 0\r\nJ (total angular) = 0.0    C (charge parity) = 0      P (space parity) = ?\r\n    Quarks: dB\r\n    Antiparticle status: Full (antiparticle name: B~0)\r\n```\r\n\r\nAny preferences @henryiii and @HDembinski ?\r\n", "created_at": "2019-02-01T13:57:27Z", "updated_at": "2019-02-01T22:18:05Z", "closed_at": "2019-02-01T22:18:00Z", "merged_at": "2019-02-01T22:18:00Z", "merge_commit_sha": "1c918fa912a38df63876989a2501b234c63648b6", "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [], "milestone": null, "draft": false, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/scikit-hep/particle/pulls/46/commits", "review_comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/scikit-hep/particle/pulls/46/comments", "review_comment_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/scikit-hep/particle/pulls/comments{/number}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/scikit-hep/particle/issues/46/comments", "statuses_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/scikit-hep/particle/statuses/22796d96bb7a26a72ba2cf0c90da58cab231bbfe", "head": {"label": "scikit-hep:eduardo-add-lifetime", "ref": "eduardo-add-lifetime", "sha": "22796d96bb7a26a72ba2cf0c90da58cab231bbfe", "user": {"login": "scikit-hep", "id": 23454624, "node_id": "MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjIzNDU0NjI0", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/23454624?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/scikit-hep", "html_url": "https://github.com/scikit-hep", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/scikit-hep/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/scikit-hep/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/use